item.title: TF2 Interactive| A Heavy's 2fort Adventure: START HERE
item.description:
TF2 Interactive| A Heavy's 2fort Adventure: START HERE
PLEASE READ THIS FIRST A Heavy's 2fort Interactive Adventure: The fat man finally leaves his happy home and embarks on an adventure...in 2fort? Trust your instincts and guide the heavy to a happy ending! If not, well, that's okay too. I've come up with so many taglines for this machinima, here's a couple: Making a bad map even worse If you think 2fort couldn't get any worse... If you hated 2fort then, you'll still hate it now! If you hate 2fort, then this video is for you! Can't play TF2 because you have a crappy computer? Well you're in luck! If you like playing sniper, then you'll love this point and click adventure! An interactive adventure you can play with one hand and do naughty things with the other! You know this is going to be awful when "2fort" is in the title! OK, that's enough of that. Well, it's finally here! My very first Machinima! And it's interactive too. It took me a while of planning, writing, and editing to get all of it done. Very hard work indeed, almost two months of planning/organizing. I really couldn't decide which version I wanted to upload so I've included both: one which was how the machinima was originally intended, and the other with two narrators guiding the viewer while providing colorful commentary. Both are very good, and provide a different experience to the viewer, so I hope you guys will try em all. Please be kind, it's my first machinima. Thank you guys, and Enjoy!
